WEBVTT

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:02.816
she said, "Always-on transformation?

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:04.920
That sounds exhausting."

00:02:05.640 --> 00:02:07.936
And that may be
exactly what you're thinking --

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.536
and you would be right.

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:14.696
Particularly if we continue to approach
the transformation of organizations

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.080
the way we always have been.

00:02:16.920 --> 00:02:19.336
But because we can't hide,

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:21.056
we need to sort out two things.

00:02:21.080 --> 00:02:22.296
First,

00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:25.056
why is transformation so exhausting?

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.840
And second, how do we fix it?

